    {
      "jp": "旅の前に、りきぞうは毎日、家の近くでよく自転車に乗りました。何回も、力を出して、長い道を走りました。二回転んで、また起きて乗りました。京都までの道は長そうです。むずかしそうです。でも、力を出して、今回は京都まで行くことにしました。",
      "en": "Before the journey, every day Rikizo often rode his bicycle near home. Many times he gathered his strength and rode along long stretches of road. He fell twice, got back up, and kept riding. The road to Kyoto looked long. It looked difficult. But he gathered his strength, and this time he decided to go all the way to Kyoto.",
